title: Owner of Group cannot access Group
body:
Hello, I have read numerous posts on the forums about summoners not being able to see and or even access their own clubs. I am one of these summoners! Maybe Riot can give it a good ol' poke or boop. 

IGN: Graphx
Group Name: Composite
Tag: 607

If any other information is needed I am willing to help in anyway I can. Thanks!

replies.body: Poked and Booped! :D   Should be okay now, thanks for reaching out.  :D Let me know if you run into any issues!
